                    <button class="faq-question">What cybersecurity certifications do your team hold?</button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Our cybersecurity team includes Certified Information Systems Security Professionals (CISSP), Certified Ethical Hackers (CEH), and Offensive Security Certified Professionals (OSCP). We also have specialists certified in ISO 27001 implementation.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">Can you provide armed guards if needed?</button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
